<div id="about_middle_1" class="about_page_article">
    <div class="about_text_content upper_window">
        <div class="about_content">
            <h3>What is mapMap?</h3>
            <p> mapMap is an interactive online leisure guide for sharing videos and images of great activities.
            Our aim is to encourage people to engage <strong> together </strong> in <strong> athletic </strong>
            actions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about_text_content lower_window">
        <div class="about_content">
            <h3>Ok nice! But how?</h3>
            <p>Don`t worry! It is very simple. There are only four steps required to share your experience with other people:</p>
            <p> <a class="create-account"> 1. Create an account </a> </p>
            <p> <a class="select-resource"> 2. Select the desired resource </a> </p>
            <p> <a class="specify-details"> 3. Specify the details of your image or video </a> </p>
            <p> <a class="add-track"> 4. Add a track if you want</a> </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="about_line_side" class="line-side"></div>
    <div id="about_line_middle" class="line"></div>
    <svg version="1.1" id="about_marker_side" class="about_marker" viewBox="0 0 56.629 52.113">
