</div>

<div id="about_middle_2" class="about_page_article">
    <div id="create-step" class="about_text_content upper_window">
        <div class="about_content">
            <h3>1. Create an account</h3>
            <p> In order to upload a video or an image it is necessary to create a user-account: </p>
            <p> 1. New mapMap account </p>
            <p> 2. Sign up with Facebook </p>
            <a href="http://mapmap.mediacube.at/users/sign_up" > Link to Register </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="select-step" class="about_text_content lower_window">
        <div class="about_content">
            <h3> 2. Select the desired resource </h3>
            <p> After the login you can choose between tree: </p>
            <p> 1. Image upload </p>
            <p> 2. Youtube- or Vimeo-video integration</p>
            <p> 3. Local video upload </p>
            <a href="http://mapmap.mediacube.at/resource_steps/select" > Link to select resource </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="about_middle_2_content">
        <h3> Why mapMap? </h3>
        <ul>
            <li> Discover new free time activities </li>
            <li> Get together </li>
            <li> Meet like-minded people </li>
            <li> Do sport! </li>
            <li> Exchange know-how </li>
            <li> goodbye boredom! </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div id="about_line_middle_top" class="line"></div>
    <div id="about_line_middle_bottom" class="line"></div>
    <svg version="1.1" id="about_marker_middle_2" class="about_marker" viewBox="0 0 52.113 66.046">
        <path fill="#FFFFFF" d="M26.057,0C11.666,0,0,11.666,0,26.057c0,12.096,8.244,22.264,19.419,25.2l1.501,3.349l5.131,11.44
