    </svg>
</div>

<div id="about_middle_3" class="about_page_article">
    <div id="detail-step" class="about_text_content upper_window">
        <div class="about_content">
            <h3>3. Specify the details of your image or video </h3>
            <p> As a third step you can add information to your video or image.
            If you add meaningful tags to your resource, other users will find
            it more easily and can spread your awesome video or image!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="track-step" class="about_text_content lower_window">
        <div class="about_content">
            <h3> 4. Add a track if you want </h3>
            <p> As a last step you are free to add a route to your resource. Here you can either
            upload a GPX-file, or draw a track on your own. Check it out! </p>
        </div>
    </div>
